    <abstract lang="eng" displayLabel="Abstract">This polygon shapefile contains glacier outlines for the Southern Andes region. These data also include an ancillary CSV file containing all hypsometric data. This layer is part of the Randolph Glacier Inventory (6.0).</abstract>
    <abstract lang="eng" displayLabel="Purpose">The Randolph Glacier Inventory (RGI 6.0) is a global inventory of glacier outlines. It is supplemental to the Global Land Ice Measurements from Space initiative (GLIMS). Production of the RGI was motivated by the Fifth Assessment Report of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC AR5).</abstract>
